data.description: Welcome Home! This beautiful stone front traditional style single family home features 5 bedrooms 3 full bathrooms and a 2 car garage with plenty of more parking on the driveway!   As you walk up the front porch & enter this sun-filled gorgeous home you will notice the beautiful light hardwood floors throughout this main level, which then opens up to the huge high ceiling living room and dinning room combo! As you enter the kitchen you'll notice the gorgeous gourmet stainless steel appliances with the beautiful dark brown cabinets & grey granite countertops! If you like to feel warm no worries, as this property is also equipped with a wood burning fireplace so you can stay warm and watch the snowfall on the back patio which is a great size for entertaining  guests! On this main level you will find 3 bedrooms 2 full bathrooms, including the huge primary bedroom that has a nice size walk in closet and a huge ensuite that features a double vanity sink, a soaker tub, and a shower. You'll also find the laundry on this level that has a brand new washer & dryer(included)!  The lower level features 2 generous sized bedrooms and 1 full bathroom and a family space & the convenient access to the garage which has more than enough space to use for storage or a possible in house gym set up! This property is conveniently located in Beltsville MD less than 10 min from major shopping centers and restaurants/stores such as Ikea, Costco, Starbucks, Best Buy. As well as major highways & roads like I-95, 295, Route 1, & I-495! This property has it all and won't last long!
